For more crazy ink and the BEST animal tattoos on the internet follow @ridnelstattoo and book your appointments! HURRY he’s almost booked for the ENTIRE 2022 🤯 DONT MISS OUT ON GREATNESS 🔥 @ridnelstattoo @ridnelstattoo @ridnelstattoo

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Mike Holston in Miami, Florida. May be an image of text.

node.text:
Praying for all my dawgs this morning 🇨🇺
I’ve grown mad love for my Hispanic friends around the world over my lifetime but particularly Cubans in Miami this shit hits different when you see the pain in their eyes and voices ! We stand with yall and pray and fight for your freedom just like we do ours 🖤👊🏾

If y’all be out eating 🍽 at Cuban spots or drinking Cuban coffee or dancing to Cuban music or smoking Cuban cigars or anything along those lines …support your homies in need …protect your neighbors and fight for them as you do yourself and for yours ! 

God bless you all and anyways i can help or any non profits to help hit me up ! 

#SOSCUBA

LONG STORY SHORT …..FREE MY AMIGOS…
All of us 🖤👊🏾
